&lt;h3 id="challah-3-loaves">Challah (3 loaves)&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Ingredients&lt;/strong> &lt;br>&lt;br>
1 Tbs yeast&lt;br>
1.5 C warm water&lt;br>
3 eggs&lt;br>
~5-6 cups flour (you can do all white, half-half, or 1/4 whole wheat)&lt;br>
1 TBs salt&lt;br>
1/3 C oil&lt;br>
1/2 C sugar &lt;br>&lt;br>&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>